frus:attachment.p:
Standard displacement in tons and metric tons; the principal dimensions,
                        namely, length at water-line, extreme beam at or below water-line and main
                        draft at standard displacement;

Standard displacement in tons and metric tons; the principal dimensions, namely, length at water-line, extreme beam at or below water-line, mean draft at standard displacement, as well as the following information regarding the armament installed on board the vessel at the date of delivery and forming part of the vessel’s normal armament:
number and calibre of guns
number and calibre of torpedo tubes;
number of bomb throwers;
number of machine-guns.
